Description: Provides functions for analyzing and visualizing results from linear 
    mixed-effects models (lme4). Includes tools for estimated marginal means (emmeans), 
    pairwise contrasts, change analysis (difference of differences), residual diagnostics, 
    and automated Word report generation. Designed for longitudinal research studies.
